How has the pandemic impacted the field of Artificial Intelligence? What are the latest trends for AI in the industry? How can I identify business opportunities with my AI technology?

Join us and leading AI industry experts in Healthcare, Mobility, Cloud-Computing, AI Assistant, Robotics and Automation, and more at the one-day Berkeley AI Summit to learn about Artificial Intelligence, its latest applications in the industry, and how it shapes the society we live in today.

Lunch and refreshments included.

Event time: Oct 1st, 9am - 4pm
Registration Link: https://www.eventbrite.com/e/berkeley-ai-summit-tickets-168832505569?discount=CSGSA
Use code ‘CSGSA’ for a student discount!
Presented by: Haas Data Science Club
